				\begin{document}$$\le 30\%$$\end{document}≤30% as a proxy for poor vegetation health conditions. Subsequently, we inferred the drought-affected vegetation activities as percentage of Central European area (shown in a rectangular box in Fig. 1g) exhibiting VHI \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
